</desc><license>Unknown</license><categories>navigation</categories><category>navigation</category><web></web><source></source><tracker></tracker><marketversion></marketversion><marketvercode>1</marketvercode><package><version>1.0</version><versioncode>1</versioncode><apkname>com.prado.gpssim-v1.apk</apkname><hash type="sha256">88e8afbdce57197e826679997fcfe96451f87b4efa4c279ddc4be7201a8228fe</hash><size>2461357</size><sdkver>26</sdkver><targetSdkVersion>35</targetSdkVersion><added>2026-03-22</added><sig>63ad5bf8645b201a8c600594fbd148be</sig><permissions>ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION,ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION,FOREGROUND_SERVICE,FOREGROUND_SERVICE_LOCATION,INTERNET,POST_NOTIFICATIONS,com.prado.gpssim.DYNAMIC_RECEIVER_NOT_EXPORTED_PERMISSION</permissions></package></application><application id="com.troyj.swiftwhisperandroidapp"><id>com.troyj.swiftwhisperandroidapp</id><added>2026-03-22</added><lastupdated>2026-03-22</lastupdated><name>Swift Whisper</name><summary>Whisper speech recognition benchmark with Vulkan GPU acceleration</summary><desc>Swift Whisper Android is a benchmark and test harness for whisper.cpp speech recognition on Android devices. It downloads whisper models on first launch and runs transcription benchmarks using Vulkan GPU acceleration on supported hardware.

Features:
- Vulkan GPU-accelerated inference on physical ARM64 devices
- Automatic model download with progress (tiny.en, large-v3-turbo-q5_0)
- Per-iteration benchmark timing with live progress display
- Correct JFK transcript verification against expected output
- CPU fallback on emulators (MoltenVK detected and skipped)

Built with Swift for Android via swift-whisper, a cross-platform SwiftPM wrapper around whisper.cpp.</desc><license>Unknown</license><categories>audio</categories><category>audio</category><web></web><source>https://github.com/TroyJ/swift-whisper</source><tracker>https://github.com/TroyJ/swift-whisper/issues</tracker><author>TroyJ</author><marketversion></marketversion><marketvercode>4</marketvercode><package><version>1.004</version><versioncode>4</versioncode><apkname>com.troyj.swiftwhisperandroidapp-v4.apk</apkname><hash type="sha256">10833f8082db5c6135bd5eaffca4748522f4c5f2451f1738ce5ea8e758c45a9a</hash><size>20947663</size><sdkver>28</sdkver><targetSdkVersion>36</targetSdkVersion><added>2026-03-22</added><sig>c5799abc78e85150d8a32ce9253a09f2</sig><permissions>INTERNET</permissions><nativecode>arm64-v8a</nativecode></package><package><version>1.003</version><versioncode>3</versioncode><apkname>com.troyj.swiftwhisperandroidapp-v3.apk</apkname><hash type="sha256">6237c5a810a563c902c1f02326cd4747bf46190929434a41a7fc0bb2c301355e</hash><size>20947663</size><sdkver>28</sdkver><targetSdkVersion>36</targetSdkVersion><added>2026-03-22</added><sig>c5799abc78e85150d8a32ce9253a09f2</sig><permissions>INTERNET</permissions><nativecode>arm64-v8a</nativecode></package><package><version>0.2.0</version><versioncode>2</versioncode><apkname>com.troyj.swiftwhisperandroidapp-v2.apk</apkname><hash type="sha256">65f00fdd6c77176386a64505d8a7feb1ff2f6db36089820dc0d9d16f4be11f24</hash><size>20946071</size><sdkver>28</sdkver><targetSdkVersion>36</targetSdkVersion><added>2026-03-22</added><sig>c5799abc78e85150d8a32ce9253a09f2</sig><permissions>INTERNET</permissions><nativecode>arm64-v8a</nativecode></package><package><version>0.1.0</version><versioncode>1</versioncode><apkname>com.troyj.swiftwhisperandroidapp-v1.apk</apkname><hash type="sha256">606dcb0bbb2fae57313981d7e94d25de123f5b16da475325c1198823d1f93c29</hash><size>20946071</size><sdkver>28</sdkver><targetSdkVersion>36</targetSdkVersion><added>2026-03-22</added><sig>c5799abc78e85150d8a32ce9253a09f2</sig><permissions>INTERNET</permissions><nativecode>arm64-v8a</nativecode></package></application><application id="com.prado.treeviewer"><id>com.prado.treeviewer</id><added>2026-03-07</added><lastupdated>2026-03-22</lastupdated><name>Tree Viewer</name><summary>v1.073 - Live overlay of the Android accessibility tree for debugging.</summary><desc>Tree Viewer is a developer tool that uses Android's AccessibilityService to display the UI tree of the current screen as a live overlay.

Features:
- Left-half overlay showing the full accessibility tree with indentation
- Tags for clickable, editable, scrollable, and long-clickable elements
- Text content and content descriptions displayed inline
- Right-half overlay with interactive blocks for clickable elements
- Blocks show color-coded action availability (click/long-click)
- Page up/down navigation for the log view
- Show/hide toggle for the right-side overlay
- Pass-through touch on the log overlay (taps reach the app underneath)
- Auto-refreshes on screen content changes with debounce

Permissions:
- Draw over other apps (SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW) — for the overlay display
- Accessibility Service — to read the UI tree

This app is intended for developers and accessibility testers. It does not collect, store, or transmit any data.
